  <brief_title>SPYRAL HTN-ON MED Study</brief_title>
  <official_title>Global Clinical Study of Renal Denervation With the Symplicity Spyral™ Multi-electrode Renal Denervation System in Patients With Uncontrolled Hypertension on Standard Medical Therapy (SPYRAL HTN-ON MED)</official_title>
